title: Nikki Glaser
itunes:title: Nikki Glaser
description:
Nikki Glaser is back on Good For You a third time talking about Uber murder, Whitney’s weird kink, how absurdly long it takes Nikki to roll a joint, and Taylor Swift.  Nikki also tells Whitney about everyone who talked shit about her.  Plus, the show opens with Whitney's plea to the team holding Britney Spears hostage.  Nikki's show FBOY ISLAND premieres on HBO Max July 29th.  

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
